body.p:
A combo box is used to present and edit the value of an attribute or an element. 
      oxy_combobox. This type of form control supports the following properties:

.
          For the Combo box form control, its value has to be combo;






;

;

editable - this property accepts the true and
            false values. The true value generates an
          editable combo-box that allows you to insert other values than the proposed ones. The
            false value generates a combo-box that only accepts the proposed
          values;

;

;

. To make the Combo-box form control inherit its font from its parent element, set the
            fontInherit property to true;

;This property is available only for read-only Combo boxes (Combo boxes that
            have the editable property set to false).

.
